metadata.name: Block Quest PassKey #1/200
metadata.description:
PassKey#02 allows entry to the token gated "Area 22" of Flagship

Add this NFT in your wallet connected to your Spatial.io account.

Enter Flagship Area-22 at this link

https://www.spatial.io/s/FLAGSHIP-Area-22-636f7ec7e051b600011c64be?share=2565670172455236298

The further you venture in Flagship Outer Worlds, the more you need to expect the unexpected. 

There are always some, that can venture further. For those willing, there may be gold at the end of the rainbow. It won't be as simple as collecting though. 

Solve the clue, to reveal the location of PassKey#3.

Good Luck.  
etherstu
